dataset.title: An annotated catalog of the primary type material of Myriapoda deposited in the Florida State Collection of Arthropods in Gainesville, FL, USA

abstract.para: This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Keller, Oliver, Dunn, Ann, Soto-Adames, Felipe (2023): An annotated catalog of the primary type material of Myriapoda deposited in the Florida State Collection of Arthropods in Gainesville, FL, USA. Zootaxa 5293 (2): 230-250, DOI: 10.11646/zootaxa.5293.2.2, URL: http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.5293.2.2
